{
  "texts": [
    "LLMs might produce an instructional resource by gathering textual information from many sources.",
    "A few applications that machine language can enable are chatbots, emotional detection, translation, summarization, and advances in various industries, including banking, healthcare, and education.One advantage of LLM is that one can work in various language-related businesses without completing further training.",
    "However, they are less useful in data analysis and evaluation because of their associations with several problems, such as biases and ethics issues [67].",
    "Information systems [68], which include a variety of sources such as Wikipedia, newspapers, documents, and social media, are frequently used as the subject of the LLM.",
    "Recognizing language patterns and relationships is essential for individuals to complete tasks, participate in conversations, and write effectively."
  ]
}